---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Research Workflow Guidebook
description: Choose a language, then move from setup to writing and GitHub-based collaboration.
lang: en
langSwitch:
  url: /ko/
  label: 한국어
pageClass: page-landing
---
<main>
  <section class="landing-hero">
    <div class="wrap hero-grid">
      <div class="hero-copy-block">
        <h1>Choose a language, then build a research workflow that actually holds up.</h1>
        <p class="hero-copy">
          This site is being rebuilt as an editorial guidebook for researchers using LaTeX,
          VS Code, Git, and GitHub. The new structure keeps the public URLs stable while
          making the core bilingual path easier to maintain.
        </p>
        <div class="button-row">
          <a class="button button-primary" href="/">English</a>
          <a class="button button-secondary" href="/ko/">한국어</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <aside class="hero-panel panel">
        <p class="eyebrow">Recent Updates</p>
        {% if updates.currentBuild %}
          <h2 class="hero-panel-title">{{ updates.currentBuild.title }}</h2>
        {% endif %}
        <dl class="updates-list">
          {% for item in updates.completed %}
            {% if loop.index <= 2 %}
              <div>
                <dt>{{ item.date }}</dt>
                <dd>
                  {% if item.url %}
                    <a href="{{ item.url }}">{{ item.title }}</a>
                  {% else %}
                    {{ item.title }}
                  {% endif %}
                </dd>
              </div>
            {% endif %}
          {% endfor %}
        </dl>
        <a class="text-link" href="/updates/">More updates →</a>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="editorial-band">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="section-heading">
        <h2>Route Map</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-grid">
        {% for section in navigation.sections %}
          <a class="feature-card panel" href="{{ section.url.en }}">
            <div class="card-logo-row">
              {% if section.key == "start-here" %}
                <img class="card-logo" src="/assets/images/LaTeX_project_logo_bird.svg.png" alt="LaTeX">
                <img class="card-logo" src="/assets/images/Visual_Studio_Code_1.35_icon.svg.png" alt="VS Code">
              {% elif section.key == "writing-in-vs-code" %}
                <img class="card-logo" src="/assets/images/Visual_Studio_Code_1.35_icon.svg.png" alt="VS Code">
              {% elif section.key == "git-github" %}
                <img class="card-logo" src="/assets/images/Visual_Studio_Code_1.35_icon.svg.png" alt="VS Code">
                <img class="card-logo" src="/assets/images/GitHub-Mark.png" alt="GitHub">
              {% endif %}
            </div>
            <p class="card-kicker">{{ section.kicker.en }}</p>
            <h3>{{ section.title.en }}</h3>
            <p>{{ section.summary.en }}</p>
          </a>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>
